    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A group of World Wide Web pages usually associated with a particular subject and connected via hyperlinks, made available online by an institution, company, government, or other organization.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
